{"tid":463763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［講下姐］加泰女議長被控叛亂罪，辯稱：「獨立公投只是做樣」","createTime":"2017-11-09T23:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T09:38:31.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fb68b385f2be128f9e33a21fb689789724ae98af","tid":463763,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:28:58.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰羅尼亞前議會女議長福卡德利，以及五名前議員，在最高法院進行聆訊。法官最終以她涉嫌犯下叛亂罪，下令將福卡德利還押，除非她付出15萬歐元（逾136萬港元）保釋金。 <br />\n<br />\n福卡德利回應檢察官提問時指出，議會所作的獨立宣言沒有法律約束力，10月1日的獨立公投也只是象徵式，被指是希望避免被扣押。據報檢察官要求法官以叛亂罪名，拘留福卡德利及另外3名前議員，而且不准保釋。但最後法官決定定下保釋金額。福卡德利一經定罪，將面臨30年監禁。 <br />\n<br />\n身處布魯塞爾等待被引渡的加泰自治區前主席普伊格蒙特，以及4名前閣員聯署，在社交網站上呼籲選民在下月的自治區議會選舉中，支持獨派候選人。西班牙首相拉霍伊則表示，希望選民履行作為西班牙人和歐洲人的義務。他指出這次選舉結果將會決定很多事，強調政府堅持歐盟價值觀，包括尊重法律、民主等，又認為多數加泰羅尼亞民眾反對獨立。 <br />\n<br />\n歐盟委員會主席容克則重申對拉霍伊的支持，更指民族主義浪潮損害歐盟在國際舞台上以團結聲音發聲的努力。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171110/mobile/bknint-20171110052652141-1110_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171110%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171110052652141-1110_17011_001.html&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNvxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f4a7ef86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171110/mobile/bknint-20171110052652141-1110_17011_001.html</a><br />\n開始淆底了"},{"pid":"5b470ecde8656cd8af2f3f4d56ea9a9cba971a79","tid":463763,"uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:31:54.000Z","msg":"原來加泰都係「講獨」派"},{"pid":"74c7bb367212c62153ac68044fdb15262e08cad3","tid":463763,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42cf3eabe8c03765842a52de4c3be98c1b62f2ef","tid":463763,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:32:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母樓主成日改新聞引啲五毛入嚟<br />\n兩個公投效果一樣<br />\n但一發動真既即刻俾人拉<br />\n重點樣知結果呀？"},{"pid":"a01ffdc4e938449f8abf985569a73ff0a854a9b9","tid":463763,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加泰人心中加泰已經獨立左,並唔需要你西班牙承認,心中獨立先最重要</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/083223_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F083223_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1d3cde14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beb1d3ff015c8d9e626d5ed11d7642c45e6da82f","tid":463763,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"三十年當判廿年<br />\n三十歲入去，五十歲出返來<br />\n為左班左膠值得嗎"},{"pid":"c2c7c5e83bc5a2d63b2c4d5476e5d676ba0dd63f","tid":463763,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:59:41.000Z","msg":"家下獨立當玩？"},{"pid":"e11f694508bb57816a761d8188a9df606cc0da57","tid":463763,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:07:16.000Z","msg":"連西班牙政府都對抗不了<br />\n<br />\n香港人要對付中國政府更難"},{"pid":"f5732fa46307e244e372c92928d6adc6e57fc169","tid":463763,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連西班牙政府都對抗不了<br />\n<br />\n香港人要對付中國政府更難</blockquote><br />\n仲未諗到世界各國有邊個有能力設軍香港而唔會被解放軍趕走<br />\n強如美國，都無咩可能打持久戰"},{"pid":"4a19ef7840f39c21d0b51ba56d7cf368fddb9e1a","tid":463763,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63677b61d9820ae09d7f3de2ef47cb477517f2dc","tid":463763,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\